oai_dc:dc.dc:title: AAA Club Building, 1959
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the Nashville Middle Tennessee Automobile Club (AAA) building, 14 September 1959. The building site was located on Parcel F of the Captiol Hill Redevelopment Project. Photographed by Jerry Hiland of the Nashville Housing Authority. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
